@base = http://localhost:8080/api

### 1. REGISTER
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ali",
  "lastName": "Huseynli",
  "email": "adminpass@gmail.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### 2. LOGIN
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ali@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}


### 3. GET COURSES
GET {{base}}/courses/size/10/page/1

### 4. ENROLLMENTS
